          {
            "title": "While Loops",
            "id": 126906,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para controlar o número de vezes que um loop <code>while</code> se repete, começamos com uma variável definida para um número. Chamamos essa variável de <strong>variável contador</strong>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" counter = \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>1</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "While Loops",
            "id": 126907,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Então, usamos uma comparação na condição para comparar a variável contador a um número. Neste caso, <code>counter &lt; 4</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" counter = \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" counter &lt; \" /><text value=\"4\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" {}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"29\" /><option startIndex=\"30\" endIndex=\"31\" /><option startIndex=\"32\" endIndex=\"33\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>counter</code> seguido de <code>&lt;</code> e finalmente <code>4</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "While Loops",
            "id": 126908,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Dentro do bloco de código, fazemos a condição retornar <code>false</code> e paramos o loop incrementando a variável de contagem. Tente com <code>counter += 1</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" counter = \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" counter &lt; \" /><text value=\"4\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(counter)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" counter += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"53\" endIndex=\"65\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>counter += 1</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Changing the condition",
            "id": 126909,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Mudar a condição informa ao loop quando parar. Por exemplo, mudar a condição para <code>counter &lt; 10</code>.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" counter = \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" counter &lt; \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(counter)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" counter += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"4\" /></content></option><option startIndex=\"32\" endIndex=\"34\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"1\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"2\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"5\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"6\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"7\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"8\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"9\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>10</code>.</p></body></html>"
