            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Como todo o bloco de código é executado, a ordem em que você escreve o código afeta o que o console exibe. Coloque <code>counter += 1</code> primeiro para exibir de <code>6</code> a <code>10</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" counter = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" counter &lt; \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" counter += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(counter)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"38\" endIndex=\"50\" /><option startIndex=\"52\" endIndex=\"66\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"6\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"7\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"8\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"9\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"10\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>counter += 1</code> seguido de <code>print(counter)</code>.</p></body></html>"
